<section class="ss-demo-page">
  <div class="ss-demo-hero">
    <span class="ss-demo-hero__pill">Demo Dashboard</span>
    <h1>Preview how a private merch store is managed.</h1>
    <p>This shows the admin side without allowing real changes. Visitors can understand the workflow, then create their own live store.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ss-demo-entry ss-demo-entry--subtle">
    <div class="ss-demo-entry__shell">
      <span class="ss-demo-entry__kicker">Raptors Demo Store</span>
      <h2>Store dashboard preview</h2>
      <p>Share the store, preview products, understand admin/member roles, and see what tools are available after a real store is created.</p>
      <div class="ss-demo-preview-strip">
        <div class="ss-demo-mini"><strong>Storefront</strong><span>Open the customer-facing collection and products in locked demo mode.</span></div>
        <div class="ss-demo-mini"><strong>Admin tools</strong><span>Buttons are visible but disabled for demo safety.</span></div>
        <div class="ss-demo-mini"><strong>Products</strong><span>Preview generated products without allowing checkout.</span></div>
        <div class="ss-demo-mini"><strong>Sharing</strong><span>Show how QR and link sharing will feel.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ss-demo-entry__actions">
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--dark" href="/collections/raptors-3978?demo=true">Open Demo Store</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--light ss-demo-disabled" href="#">Share Store</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--light ss-demo-disabled" href="#">Edit Products</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--gold" href="/pages/request-storefront-form">Create My Store</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "SS Demo Dashboard Page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "SS Demo Dashboard Page" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
